strings.safetyquiz-intro: Test your online safety knowledge in this quiz and earn a FREE online safety sweater for your penguin.
strings.safetyquiz-title: Take the Be Cool, Be Heard, Be Safe Quiz!
strings.safetyquiz-welldone: You really know your stuff about online safety and how to be cool, be heard, and be safe!
strings.safetyquiz-wrongbody: That wasn't quite right. Do you want to try the safety quiz again?
strings.safetyquiz-q0-question: Which of these is safe to share online?
strings.safetyquiz-q1-question: Who should you tell if you experience something online that bothers you?
strings.safetyquiz-q1-answer3: A parent, teacher, or trusted adult
strings.safetyquiz-q2-question: To be safe, treat people the way you want to be treated.
strings.safetyquiz-q3-question: It's okay to share your password with:
strings.safetyquiz-q4-question: It's always a good idea to ask talk to a parent before joining a social website.
strings.safetyquiz-q5-question: When creating online profiles, choose names that...
strings.create-choose-age:
Heya! I'm Rookie, and welcome to Club Penguin Plus!
Before you can create your penguin, I need to know, how old are you?
This is so we can prioritize the safety of our players.
strings.create-choose-username: Woah! That's cool! This next step is fun - What do you want your Penguin's Name to be? Remember not to use your real name, or anything personally indentifiable.
strings.create-under-13:
Cool! Go and ask a parent or guardian to help you with creating your account.

Parents, click OK when you're ready!
strings.create-tos: Great! Now, before you can create your account, you need to read and agree to our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy.
strings.create-tos-parent: Great! Now, before you can create your account, your parent or guardian needs to read and agree to our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy.
strings.create-username-too-short: Sorry, but your username must be at least 3 characters long.
strings.create-username-too-long: Sorry, but your username must be less than 12 characters long.
strings.create-username-taken: Sorry, but that username is already taken. Try another one!
strings.create-choose-color:
Awesome! Now, {args[0]}, what color do you want your penguin to be? You can choose from any of these colors.
Click 'OK' when you're ready!
strings.create-choose-password: Now, you need to choose a password. Make sure it's at least 6 characters long, and secure. You can use letters, numbers, and symbols.
strings.create-password-too-short: Sorry, but your password must be at least 6 characters long.
strings.create-password-too-long: Sorry, but your password must be less than 12 characters long.
strings.create-passwords-dont-match: Sorry, but your passwords don't match. Try again!
strings.create-choose-email: Great! Now, enter your email address. We'll send you a link to activate your account.
strings.create-choose-email-parent: Great! Now, ask your parent or guardian to enter their email address. We'll send them a link to activate your account.
strings.create-email-invalid: Sorry, but that doesn't look like a valid email address.
strings.create-unhandled-error: Sorry, but there was an error creating your account. Please try again later. If this problem persists, please contact support.
strings.create-email-taken: Sorry, but that email address is already in use.
strings.create-account-created: Awesome! Your account has been created. Check your email for a link to activate your account.
strings.create-account-created-parent: Awesome! Your account has been created. We've sent your parent or guardian an email with a link to activate your account.
strings.registerkeysuccess: You now have access to the beta!
strings.registerkeyfail: Something went wrong. Please check your key, and make sure an account with that username exists.
strings.moderator-body: If someone is breaking the rules, click on their penguin, then click the 'M' to report them to a moderator. You can also click on the skull to ignore them
strings.kick-header: A moderator has removed you from the server.
strings.kick-body: Please remember to follow the Club Penguin Plus rules.

strings.warning-body: If you break a Club Penguin Plus rule again, you may be banned.

strings.recruitment-intro:
{args[0]}, this island needs you.
Become an agent and help protect Club Penguin Plus.
Will you take up the challenge?
strings.recruitment-accepted:
Welcome to the Elite Penguin Force, Agent {args[0]}.
Here's your spy phone - your most important tool.
Keep it on you to receive your orders.
strings.recruitment-accept:
We look forward to working with you, agent.
Enter the command room to hone your skills.
And good luck.
strings.recruitment-reject:
Very well. Carry on.
If you change your mind, give us a call.
